data.description: In the middle of the Klein District is a home that is a perfect fit for any homebuyer.  This 3 bedroom home creates a cozy home feeling as you walk in.  The Master Bedroom and second bedroom can serve as an adjoining  nursery or an office.  The sunken living room has the perfect touch for entertainment. The kitchen has beautiful granite tops    and is very spacious open to the breakfast room.  New A/C was installed in 2021 and new roof was installed in 2015 in addition to new backyard fence just installed in 2023. House also has solar panels. There is a spacious yard with a nice porch in addition to shed.  A home worth every minute seeing.
